snippet.title: Exocide - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Exocide is a retro FPS with an early 00's aesthetic. Manage two powerful sets of weapons systems with extreme aggression to annihilate the swarm! Keep your maniacal robotic backpack excited with gruesome headshots, bug guts and multi-kills. It will offer full kinetic power in return.


Source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lUm7rh3oavg
Exocide on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1678350/EXOCIDE
